@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pyhpqv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(tmp + 0.56)) - (wp.abs(tmp + 0.57) * (v0 + 0.01 + v2 + 0.09)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin(wp.sin(v1 + 0.53)))
    tmp = (0.16 * v0)
    tmp = (0.47 * ((tmp + 0.91 * v1 + 0.01) - wp.cos(v1 + 0.14)))
    v1 = wp.exp((tmp * 0.14))
    v1 = 0.98
    v0 = v2
    v0 = wp.abs(0.14)
    data[tid] = v0
